Description:
Experience Bright and Stylish Docklands Living!
Central to all the amazing Docklands attractions and ideal for those who desire a light-filled and spacious apartment, this two bedroom residence in the Victoria Point complex is a stylish package ready for all buyers. With charming views including Etihad Stadium and the bay, you're moments to Docklands Park, The Hub @ Docklands, great cafes, trams, and Southern Cross Station.

Features: Secure car space, storage cage, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, on-site building manager.

Description:
Dual key, multiple opportunities
Have the best of all worlds with this unique opportunity to own a Victorian Point complex property. In fact, you can own two of them, a dual key property. You’ll have the option to rent them both out or live in one and rent out the other. Both are modern, light filled and have outstanding views of the Port Phillip Bay and the CBD. They have central heating and cooling as well as intercom entry, on-site Building Manager and concierge services.
In apartment one, you’ll find one bedroom with BIR and access to the very well sized balcony which is also accessed via the spacious living areas. There’s a stunning kitchen with stone bench tops, stainless steel appliances, glass splash backs and gas cooking as well as a European laundry complete with dryer. There’s also a luxurious separate bathroom.
Apartment two is the mini version as it is a studio, however it comes will all the required facilities including kitchen, European laundry and bathroom.
There is also a basement car park with storage, and without a doubt all you could possibly need is on your doorstep: Southern Cross Station, Etihad Stadium, Tram stops, local schools and universities, local cafes, bars and restaurants. This is a very unique opportunity, you won’t be disappointed with this one and we expect it to be snapped up quite quickly, contact us today to find out more.

Description:
Docklands Most Affordable Two Bedroom Apartment
This impressive North facing two bedroom apartment in the heart of Docklands is currently leased out fully furnished for $590 per week.
The space is free-flowing with designated space to eat, sleep, and lounge. The central living zone is split into dedicated lounge and meals areas which is adjoined by the stylish kitchen complete with a glass splashback, stone benchtop, and quality stainless steel appliances.
A private and well-sized balcony offers tremendous city views and an opportunity for daily alfresco meals and drinks. The main bedroom boasts a built-in robe and direct access to the balcony, meanwhile also enjoy a gorgeous bathroom, concealed laundry, reverse cycle cooling, secure intercom, storage cage, and secure car space.
This apartment is located in the excellent Quays complex which offers a Health Club featuring a swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium and a yoga studio. There is a Resident’s Club on Level One with a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room & cinema lounge, while there is also a rooftop garden with tennis court and BBQ dining facilities.
You’re located in the vibrant NewQuay precinct which has an assortment of restaurants and cafes to choose from. You’re also near Etihad Stadium, Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Medibank Icehouse and with the free tram zone on your door step the rest of Melbourne is in easy reach.
Please call Vicky Leong on 0452 486 860 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
Waterside Brilliance With Space and Wonderful Views
Enjoying a magnificent location next to Point Park and a wonderful example of spacious dual level living which also features impeccable style and gorgeous views, this coveted 3 bedroom + study, 2 bathroom abode is as captivating a Docklands property as you’re likely to find.
Kick off 2018 by making the wonderful Docklands switch and taking advantage of this stunning waterside location in the exclusive Yarra’s Edge precinct. Your entry leads directly into a courtyard which has amazing potential for summer entertaining. Inside, an open plan central living and dining zone has direct sight to the kitchen which is complete with stone benchtops, an island bench, and stainless steel Miele appliances.
The ground floor further benefits from a sizeable bedroom with built-in robes as well as a well-appointed dual vanity bathroom. The upper level features two further bedrooms, one with direct access to the balcony offering picturesque river and park views as well city and Southbank vistas. Upstairs also promises a dedicated study and stylish bathroom, while other extras include euro laundry, ducted heating and cooling, brand new timber floors, intercom, and two secure car spaces.
In the coveted Yarra Point complex, you have access to a 300 sqm rooftop herb garden complete with BBQ facilities, plus a residents’ lounge, gym, business centre and RekDek facilities inclusive of 25m pool, spa, sauna and fully equipped gymnasium. You’re also close to DFO shopping, Crown Casino, Spencer Street trams, Southern Cross Station, and South Wharf promenade eateries/bars including West Village NYC, Gasolina, Meat Market, Common Man, and Melbourne Public.

Seize this Lavish and Spacious Yarra’s Edge Retreat
From the clever floorplan and luxurious interiors to remarkable views of the Yarra River and parts of Southbank and the CBD, this elegant two bedroom + study, two bathroom apartment is your chance to live the modern Docklands good life.
Bright floor-to-ceiling windows, quality stone benchtops, excellent tapware, and other premium touches is what sets this residence apart from the rest. The large undercover balcony can be accessed via the spacious living and meals zones, with this special alfresco space taking in the beautiful water views with Southbank and city buildings completing the picturesque backdrop.
The opulent kitchen is also practical with an island bench and stainless steel appliances. A dedicated study has its own privacy as do both bedrooms which includes the excellent master bedroom which offers a dual vanity ensuite and another balcony. Also make the most of a gorgeous central bathroom, concealed laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, 2 secure car spaces, and access to RekDek with gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
You have super easy access to the city, Port Melbourne, Southbank, and South Melbourne, while walk to South Wharf and enjoy terrific spots including Meat Market, Common Man, West Village NYC. Also near DFO shops, Crown Casino, and Southern Cross Station.

Entertainers Delight in Tower 3!
This outstanding apartment is conveniently situated in the most sought after Yarra’s Edge.

- Spacious open plan living/dining leading onto sun filled massive entertainers terrace

Do not delay to inspect this apartment as this gem is sure to be snapped up!

Description:
Inspired ‘Array’ Living in the Exclusive Yarra’s Edge
Owning a stunning address in the Yarra’s Edge precinct while presenting a living experience filled with exemplary contemporary style and exceptional 30th floor views, this two bedroom, two bathroom apartment in the Array complex is too hard to ignore.
This brilliant corner residence is awash with amazing natural light and delivers breathtaking views that includes the wonderful city skyline and Yarra River below. Enjoy lounging and dining in the expansive central living zone, which has convenient access to a sizeable undercover balcony which is the best place to soak in the stellar views.
Preparing meals will be a cinch in the well-appointed kitchen which comes with an island bench, great cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances. The master bedroom comes with ample built-in robe storage and an ensuite, while the 2nd bedroom has easy access to the main bathroom. Other extras include a European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, and two car spaces. Residents of Array also have access to an on-site gym as well as RekDek which includes a gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
The Yarra’s Edge precinct is one of the most sought-after areas in the Docklands, with the nearby South Wharf promenade offering a variety of superb restaurants and bars such as Citizen Café and Bar, Common Man, Plus 5 Bar, and Munich Brauhaus. You’re also near the Melbourne Exhibition Centre, DFO shopping, Crown Entertainment Complex, Etihad Stadium, Polly Woodside, trams, and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
Unmatched Views and Sant’Elia Style
Situated in the boutique Sant’Elia complex which is only metres from the calming waters of Victoria Harbour, this two bedroom, two bathroom apartment is the perfect example of peaceful, spacious, and stylish Docklands living.
You’ll love sitting on the generous undercover balcony and soaking in the wonderful uninterrupted views of the harbour, Etihad Stadium, and the city. Inside, sleek timber floors flow through the sizeable living and dining zone, while the functional kitchen includes a breakfast bar and Smeg stainless steel appliances.
The master bedroom is a living experience all on its own with a study space leading out to a private balcony as well as having a walk-in robe and stylish ensuite. Other apartment features include a 2nd bedroom with BIR, impressive bathroom, European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom, secure car space, and a share of the Palladio facilities which include a health club with rooftop pool, gym, and private function area. This apartment also has 103 sqm (approx.) of total space!
Take advantage of great surrounding restaurants including Mint-o-Mustard, Solidaire, Fish Bar, Medici Docklands restaurant, and Oscars Table, while you’re also near IGA X-press supermarket, District Docklands Shopping Centre and local trams.
Please contact Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Tower 5 Living with Spectacular Views
With Docklands as your playground and this consummate apartment as your base, you’ll have everything you’ve ever desired within in the prestigious Tower 5 complex on Yarra’s Edge.
Unobstructed views of Port Philip Bay create a spectacular backdrop through the full walls of windows that surround the understated yet premium interior. The master bedroom has access to the undercover balcony and is conveniently positioned next to the gleaming central bathroom with double, fully tiled shower and separate bath. The second bedroom is light filled and located on the opposite side of the apartment for optimal privacy.
Enjoy the balcony which is an idyllic spot to entertain friends and other features include separate laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, 2 secure car spaces, and access to RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna. Walk to South Wharf Promenade with restaurants and bars including Meat Market, The Boatbuilders Yard, The General Assembly, and Plus 5 Bar. Description:
SUPERB DOCKLANDS HOME WITH BREATHTAKING VIEWS
Be swept away by the amazing views offered from this beautifully renovated home in Docklands’ Newquay. Overlooking Victoria Harbour, this sumptuous apartment has been fitted with European Oak floorboards, new kitchen, and remodelled bathrooms. Featuring floor to ceiling windows presenting fantastic panoramic views, this apartment has space, style, and quality. Offering an open plan living, dining and kitchen, this contemporary home is built for entertainment with the living room opening up to a generous balcony drinking in sensational views. Just imagine soaking in that vista with a cold drink and some cool tunes at the end of a long day.
The kitchen is a chef’s dream with an island bench, Smeg appliances, abundant cupboard space, and stone benchtops. The master bedroom has a private balcony offering brilliant views, and is complemented by a walk-in-robe with a stylish ensuite. The central bathroom continues the clean, modern theme of the apartment, with a separate shower and bath. The remaining bedrooms both come with built-in-robes and views of the marina, whilst a separate laundry rounds out this beautifully appointed home.
Split system heating & cooling, 2 secure car spaces, storage cage, and secure swipe & intercom entry complete this beautiful residence, which includes use of the swimming pool and gymnasium, making this resort style living 365 days a year.
Conveniently located in the free tram zone, and in the North Melbourne Primary School & University High School zones, and with Etihad Stadium, a world class shopping precinct, and an array of waterside restaurants and bars on your doorstep, this must see apartment is perfectly situated only minutes from the CBD and CityLink.

Description:
Yarra Edge Exclusivity
Evocative of the lifestyle for the which the Yarra Edge address is so keenly sought, the spaces of this tri-level contemporary terrace reflect sophistication in both its style and size. Open plan living on the ground level is graced by generous proportions and the added asset of dedicated street-level entry, accommodating for an abundance of possibilities - stunning third bedroom, home office, rumpus room or studio - and limited only by your desires. Superb upstairs living/dining domain underscored by immaculate hardwood floors expresses the allure of entertaining, a concept made especially enticing by gorgeous alfresco deck that's exceptionally proportioned yet entirely private. Sparkling kitchen finished in crisp cream stone boasts Miele quality and bar-style meals. Two bedrooms set above all else achieve an ambience of considerable comfort, a quality acknowledged by built-in-robes, sleek skylit bathroom and private ensuite to main. Further features including zoned heating/cooling, enormous tandem garage, euro laundry and quality finishes to all areas complement such an address as to be mere minutes from the River Esplanade's restaurants and bars, walking/cycling paths, transport and the CBD.

WATERFRONT AND BRAND NEW!
For sale By nomination
Located in the heart of NewQuay, with a promise to deliver sophisticated modern character, stunning quality, and a convenient waterside location, this 2 bed 2 bath waterfront apartment in the SOLD OUT Marina Tower development is a rare opportunity!
This building designed by DKO Architecture has the potential to become an iconic building for NewQuay, Docklands and Melbourne. Available to both local and offshore purchasers, Maximum stamp duty savings may also be applicable.
Positioned on the 24th level, this superb apartment encompasses a stylishly contemporary interior and floor-to-ceiling windows allowing for great natural light.
Additional features include:
- Quality Miele appliances,
- Open plan living and dining area,
- Views facing the harbour
- 1 carpark on title
Luxurious resort style amenities include:
- Swimming pool on level 7,
- Resident Cinema,
- Library,
- Private meeting rooms,
- Hotel restaurant, cafe and retail on the ground floor.
Ideal investment for anyone want live the dream in Docklands. Situated only moments from public transport including free trams into the CBD, various shopping options at Harbourtown, waterfront dining options, this location is second-to-none.
Estimated completion is Lat November 2017
Please call Peter Doan for more information

Description:
ABSOLUTE WATERFRONT & NEAR NEW!
A superb opportunity exists at this in-demand 5 Star address that's is the 'Concavo'. On offer is an as new luxury two bedroom two bathroom apartment perfectly poised on the 25th floor, directly facing north and towards the water.
This prestigious 'Concavo' building has set the bench-mark for all future living within the Docklands precinct. The 'never to be built out' views from this beautiful apartment could not be better as you peer from your living room or bedrooms across the water to NewQuay and beyond, the marina below or down the river to Bolte Bridge.
This breathtaking apartment comprises of two spacious bedrooms each with their own stylish bathroom, separate laundry room, a designer kitchen with stainless steel appliances, stone bench tops, and an abundance of cupboard space, living room with amazing water views, a wide balcony perfect for entertaining, ducted air conditioning/heating and two secure undercover car spaces plus storage cage.
In addition, the amenities of this luxurious building includes:
- 24 hour concierge
- Residents Lounge
- Business Centre & Board Room
- Indoor Cinema
- North facing Sky Garden facing the water, with BBQ facilities
- 25 metre indoor heated pool, spa and sauna
- Gymnasium and treatment room
Don't miss your opportunity to secure this apartment right by the waterside. Please call Peter Doan on 0423 399 999 to enquire today!

Description:
Brilliant Balance of Sleek Style and Marvellous Internal Space
An exceptional harmony of sophisticated contemporary elegance and fabulous space, this two bedroom, two bathroom residence in Tower 3 of Yarra’s Edge has the magnificent CBD and marina as your daily backdrop!
This flawless abode sits high on the 24th floor and delivers superb detail from stone surfaces, soft carpet and floor-to-ceiling windows. The expansive central living zone has designated lounge and dining spaces, with this airy hub further oozing out to the full-length north/east-facing balcony which displays some of the most spectacular skyline views in all of the Docklands.
A dazzling kitchen is ideal for home gourmands with a long breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances. The master bedroom is an excellent size and includes dual mirrored BIRs and a double vanity ensuite, meanwhile the spacious 2nd bedroom with BIRs is a few steps to the striking central bathroom. Both bedrooms also have balcony access. Also enjoy a separate laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom entry, 2 car spaces, storage cage and access to RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
The superb Yarra’s Edge precinct sits right on the banks of the iconic river and is a dream spot for owner-occupiers looking to make the Docklands change. You’re close to an array of brilliant attractions in the South Wharf area which is alive on Friday and Saturday nights, while nearby DFO Shopping, Capital City Trail, Crown Casino, public transport, and Victoria Harbour precinct via Webb Bridge is easily accessed.

Description:
WELL KEPT WATERGATE RESIDENCE WITH UPGRADED TIMBER FLOORING
A fantastic opportunity to secure this recently renovated and stylish 2 bedroom 1 bathroom apartment in the award winning Watergate Complex.
With a desirable location unmatched and packed with features and facilities, this spacious 2 bedroom will be at the top of your list.
Apartment 1004 at 8 at Waterview Walk is positioned on the 10th floor and facing the CBD. This recently upgrade 2 bedroom residence has plenty to offer:
- Large & spacious main bedroom with floor to ceiling windows, small study nook and complete with built in mirrored wardrobes.
- Additional 2nd bedroom with floor to ceiling windows facing CBD.
- Generous open plan living and dining area and direct access to a stretched balcony with dual access from master bedroom and living area.
- Recently upgraded timber flooring through out living, dining and bedrooms.
- White polish finished kitchen with plenty of cupboard storage including island bench/breakfast bar and large fridge space, SMEG stainless steel appliances including 4 burner gas cook top, range hood & dishwasher.
- Spacious bathroom with European laundry access
- Heating & Cooling.
- Secure intercom/video access.
- Secure basement parking
5 Star Facilities/Additional Features:
- Access to a very well equipped gym.
- Access to a heated pool with spa.
- Access to Sauna.
- Access to Entertainment area for guests and private functions.
Public Transport & Location:
- Free City Circle Tram at your door step.
- Short stroll to Melbourne CBD & Crown Casino.
- Within 5 minutes walk to Southern Cross Train Station & Etihad Stadium.
- Watergate is positioned between Collins St, Harbour Esp and Latrobe St tram stops.
- Walking distance to South Warf DFO.
- Close to Harbour Town Shopping Centre.
- Plenty of green parklands nearby and access to a public basketball court at the front of the building.
Property is currently leased at $510 per week unfurnished making this also a very secure and sound investment.
With a rare and unique floor plan, access to 5 star facilities and positioned in a great location, this 2 bedroom apartment at Watergate Towers should be at the top of your shopping list.
